name: Mexican Arrow Tips Black
description:
Created in the heart of Mexico City, the Enter the Brave collection explores the power of the individual, the sacrifice of many and the power of unseen gods. 

The marks of a warriors arrow embedded in sterling silver earrings with a black oxide finish. These mini earrings are brave and made for lovers and fighters.

Sterling silver earring and earring wire with oxide finish.

Width 1.5cm, length 2.5cm

Made to order. 

Shipping included.
